parameters: Are you sleeping...? Is work tough for you?
You have someone you love, don't you?

Yeah, deep down in my heart... it's about that
person.
Hehe, it's written all over your face.

They also have feelings for you. Would you like to
take a peek?

I wonder where they are and what they're doing
right now...

Ah, it's possible. However, the memories while
peeping...
Once you finish peeping, it will disappear.
Eh, if I peek, will my memories disappear?
Well, whether I peek or not, it's all the same...

Enough, enough. There are people who benefit when
you peek!

Alright, with this, you are now inside their
consciousness. You won't be able to speak, but you
will be merged with them.
If you want to return, just come back here.
Well then, have a safe journey.

Tch, go ahead and peek...!! That's what the
heavenly voice said.

Shall we take a peek? About the person you're
thinking of.

The other person is also thinking of you. Now,
what will you do?
Alright, then let's close our eyes...

Alright, with this, you are now inside their
consciousness. You won't be able to speak, but you
will be merged with them.
If you want to return, just come back here.

Tsk, let's take a peek...!! Someone is
complaining, huh.
Welcome back. Are you already going back?

I don't remember anything I've seen so far. What
should I do?
Welcome back. It seems you returned safely.
Huh, was I just peeping on Clot?

Yeah, unfortunately, I don't think I have any
memories at all.
Eh... I wonder if I'm being deceived...

Hehe, it's no big deal. If you feel like peeping
again, come back anytime.

I see. If you feel like coming back, it's good to
come here again.
I'm sorry for what I did...
